net.webpdf.ant.task.files

Class IterativeTaskFileMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.webpdf.ant.task.files.IterativeTaskFileMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<IterativeTaskFile>

    public class IterativeTaskFileMap
extends Object
implements Iterable<IterativeTaskFile>
    The TaskFileCollection collects all files, that the current webPDF task shall be executed for. An instance of this class will also provide information about the used and needed directories. It also provides a mapping from each individual source file to the intended target file name.
